ost benefiting rangers, clerics, beastlords, and possibly even int casters.  Classes might even have innate ac/effects multipliers for various armor/weapon types such as int casters getting more per AC point out of cloth based armors, but metal based armor would have higher base AC providing a nice dynamic.  Multipliers could also be based on race... maybe dwarfs are get a 1.15 bonus with an axe, .95 with a short sword, and .75 with a long sword.<br>
